    "Html": "\r\n<p>Hallo,</p>\r\n<p>in my ViewModel i add a delegatecommand to a menuitem</p>\r\n<p>But <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span>the</span> <span>method</span> <span>\r\nis never called</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"en\"><span>ViewModel:<br>\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<pre style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:13; color:black; background:white\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color:blue\">Private</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:blue\">Sub</span>&nbsp;initMenuCommands(<span style=\"color:blue\">ByVal</span>&nbsp;pSubMenuItems&nbsp;<span style=\"color:blue\">As</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#2b91af\">ObservableCollection</span>(<span style=\"color:blue\">Of</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#2b91af\">SubMenuItem</span>))\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color:blue\">For</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:blue\">Each</span>&nbsp;itm&nbsp;<span style=\"color:blue\">In</span>&nbsp;pSubMenuItems\r\n&nbsp;  &nbsp; initMenuCommands(itm.ChildMenuItems)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color:green\">itm.MenuSelected&nbsp;=&nbsp;New&nbsp;DelegateCommand(Of&nbsp;SubMenuItem)(AddressOf&nbsp;MenuSelected)</span>\r\n&nbsp;  <span style=\"color:blue\">Next</span>\r\n <span style=\"color:blue\">End</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:blue\">Sub<br><br></span><pre style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:13px; color:black; background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white\"><span style=\"color:blue\">Private</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:blue\">Sub</span>&nbsp;MenuSelected(pSubMenuItem&nbsp;<span style=\"color:blue\">As</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#2b91af\">SubMenuItem</span>)\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; ' Do anything&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<span style=\"color:blue\">End</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">Sub</span></pre>\r\n<br><span style=\"color:blue\"><br>In my View i have the following xaml-code:<br></span>\r\n<pre style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:13px; color:black; background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white\"><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">sdk</span><span style=\"color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">HierarchicalDataTemplate</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;x</span><span style=\"color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:red\">Key</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;MainMenuTemplate&quot;</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;ItemsSource</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;ChildMenuItems</span><span style=\"color:blue\">}</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:#a31515\">  </span><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Button</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;Command</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;MenuSelected</span><span style=\"color:blue\">}</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;CommandParameter</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"color:blue\">}</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&nbsp;&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:#a31515\">&nbsp;   </span><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Button.Template</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;   </span><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">ControlTemplate</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;   </span><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">StackPanel</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;Orientation</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;Horizontal&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;   </span><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Image</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;Margin</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;0,0,5,0&quot;</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;Source</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;ImageId</span><span style=\"color:blue\">,</span><span style=\"color:red\">Converter</span><span style=\"color:blue\">={</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">StaticResource</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;ImageConverter</span><span style=\"color:blue\">}}</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">/&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">TextBlock</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;Text</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;Description</span><span style=\"color:blue\">}</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;FontStyle</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;Italic&quot;</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;Foreground</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;#777&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&nbsp;/&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">StackPanel</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">ControlTemplate</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Button.Template</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:#a31515\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Button</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:#a31515\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">sdk</span><span style=\"color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">HierarchicalDataTemplate</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">&nbsp; <br></span></pre>\r\n<br>Can anyone help me<br><br>Jens<br></pre>\r\n",
